title: Assassins Creed Syndicate Update v1.31 incl DLC-CODEX
description:
C O D E X
P R E S E N T S

Assassin's Creed Syndicate - Update v1.31 incl. DLc

Release Date: 12/2015 Protection: Uplay
Discs: 1 Genre: Action

For list of changes read included patchnotes.txt

Extract
Run setup.exe and install update
Copy crack from CODEX dir to installdir
Play

Notes: New Jack the Ripper DLC has been added. Some preorder/season
pass goodies were added too. Earn them later in the game

This patch requires:

Assassins.Creed.Syndicate-CODEX
Assassins.Creed.Syndicate.Update.v1.21-CODEX

Block the game's exe in your firewall to prevent the game from
trying to go online
If you install games to your systemdrive, it may be necessary
to run this game with admin privileges instead
